"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-watch-epic-late-surge-that-saw-tatjana-smith-win-olympic-gold\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9769332556206821, \"rank\": 0.023609086984689387, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbWATCH: Epic late surge that saw Tatjana Smith win Olympic gold!\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9769332556206821, \"rank\": 0.023609086984689387, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch a replay of the epic race, and incredible finish, that saw Tatjana Smith secure SA's first Olympic gold medal in the 100m breaststroke.\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0608605153622154e-18, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coming into the 100m Olympic breaststroke final on Monday night, Tatjana Smith was the clear favourite, but she touched and turned at the 50m mark trailing in fourth place.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, a stunning late surge in the final 20m enabled her to touch the wall first in1.05.28toclaim South Africa's first gold medalat theParis Games2024.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 687, \"end\": 699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999980636858, \"rank\": 1.93613764332558e-09, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think anyone can explain it,\\\" she stated afterwards.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 804, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Like I said last night, for me the emotions were really because it took a village to get me to where I am.\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know they would have been proud even if I did not have a medal.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 979, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was really for them; I swam for everyone that's been there for me and believed with me.\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 1074, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was for our country as well, our hashtag for [Team SA's campaign] is 'For my Country'.\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1166, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1131, \"end\": 1133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0608605153622154e-18, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it really is, it's just to inspire someone at home, for them to know they are not disqualified from the race and to know that they could potentially be an Olympic champion.\\\"\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith's own Olympics tally has now grown to three, with two golds and a silver.\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One more will see her equal Chad le Clos on four, the most of any South African Olympian.\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1456, \"end\": 1468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chad le Clos\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\"}, {\"begin\": 1508, \"end\": 1516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999992518317483, \"rank\": 7.481686305932091e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her attention will next turn to defending her gold in the 200m.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been an incredible journey over the last few years as Smith once admitted she was considering walking away from the pool.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes when the expectations get too much you lose the fun and joy out of competing, and that definitely played a role in the last two years,\\\" she said during an interview last year.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's definitely been tough.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You think there is a lot of expectations but it's mostly your own.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You always think people will be disappointed if you do not pull out the same performances as before.\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2096, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You just have to give your best; you can not always be at your complete best.\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think any athlete has run, swam PBs left, right and centre every time they compete.\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2269, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can never always have the perfect race and I think it was one of the challenges after the Olympics - it's impossible for me not to expect a lot from myself.\\u00a0\\\"\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2434, \"end\": 2437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999971152661373, \"rank\": 2.8647849092214037e-06, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 2438, \"end\": 2440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"score\": 0.9976173106442721, \"rank\": 0.0020772450477073417, \"text\": \"R2\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writing positions available  Follow The South African on Facebook for the latest local and international news  Follow The South African's WhatsApp channel for the latest sport, lifestyle and local news  Follow The South African on X for the latest, breaking news  A brand new shopping mall is coming to Pretoria East, bringing major retailers and new convenience to the area.\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2662, \"end\": 2670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9999977570839889, \"rank\": 2.242921079863893e-06, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Orlando Pirates are reportedly set to welcome a new staff member i